%%{init: {'theme':'base', 'themeVariables': {'fontSize':'16px', 'actorFontSize':'16px', 'noteFontSize':'14px', 'messageFontSize':'14px'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Producer
    participant M as Mutex
    participant E as Event
    participant C1 as Consumer 1
    participant C2 as Consumer 2

    Note over C1,C2: Waiting on Event
    P->>M: Lock
    P->>P: Write work item
    P->>M: Unlock
    P->>E: Signal
    E-->>C1: Wake
    E-->>C2: Wake

    C1->>M: Lock (acquire)
    C2->>M: Lock (blocked)
    C1->>C1: Read work item
    C1->>M: Unlock

    C2->>M: Lock (acquire)
    C2->>C2: Check for work
    Note over C2: No work available
    C2->>M: Unlock
    C2->>E: Wait

    P->>M: Lock
    P->>P: Write work item
    P->>M: Unlock
    P->>E: Signal
    E-->>C2: Wake

    C2->>M: Lock
    C2->>C2: Read work item
    C2->>M: Unlock
